title: Murphy, Mets beat Cubs 5-2 for commanding 3-0 lead in NLCS
text:
> Sports Murphy, Mets beat Cubs 5-2 for commanding 3-0 lead in NLCS New York Mets' Daniel Murphy scores past Chicago Cubs catcher Miguel Montero during the seventh inning of Game 3 of the National League baseball championship series Tuesday, Oct. 20, 2015, in Chicago. Murphy scored from third on a ball hit by Lucas Duda. (AP Photo/Charles Rex Arbogast)
